s.text: p>Organizations that employ eProvisioning gain a competitive edge and access complete security by ensuring that people are kept productive from day one, and are prevented from becoming counterproductive beyond the day they leave.
p>eProvisioning radically improves people's Time-To-Productivity by transforming the disparate activities that allocate IT resources to people into a secure and automatic process.
